                "correlation_property": null
              },
              "free_text": [
                " The cross-section scale is estimated to be",
                "uncertain by 15% owing to the uncertainty in",
                "determination of the absolute oxygen content of the",
                "targets and to the uncertainty in the value of the",
                "spectrometer efficiency."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "COMMENT": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "Authors say that in their opinion the cs to higher",
